OL,5, A Ukrainian doctor has been offered a  
OL,6, house for herself and her family to    
OL,7, stay in as thanks for helping to save  
OL,8, the life of a Russian man with Covid.  
OL,10,FOlga Pantos, 42, was working as a      
OL,11,Fcardiologist in Donetsk, a             
OL,12,FRussian-occupied part of Ukraine, when 
OL,13,Fshe treated Konstantin Tarasov in 2021.
OL,15,FWhen Russia invaded Ukraine a few      
OL,16,Fmonths later he offered her the use of 
OL,17,Fhis second home in Gloucestershire.    
OL,19,FHe said it was his turn to save her and
OL,20,Furged her to come to the UK, she said. 
